<br>
I do know that at level 23 a Frair will not be soloing high oranges any more.  I have a couple of +evade and +parry items and full yellow armour and a staff that is better than the dark shod at level 23 and high oranges CRUSH me. They take 1/6 of my HP in every hit they connect on. Evade and parry are based on a blue con monster so fighting oranges cuts those down to like 1/3 of what you would see on a blue.<br>
<br>
My wife is the cleric I always group with and she starts slapping me around every single time I get agro because it suckes her power. I can wipe any caster off the face of Albion but if something has a slashing weapon I get hammered. My job is to do damage from the non-sharp end of the fight and provide heal support as needed. The sharp end is for the armsmen and they can have it. <br>
<br>
I usually group with an armsman and cleric. I heal the armsman the first couple of times to keep agro off the cleric then I wade in with a Friars Redress until it hits. Works like a charm. That way our little group can and does regularly take 2 reds. Defenders Fury and Friars Redress are your friends. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.showPrevMessage?topicID=184.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.showNextMessage?topicID=184.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=184.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.emailToFriend?topicID=184.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.threadControl?topicID=184.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=184.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm14.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=184.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b>